 Keyes, Buckinghamshire, England":"英国英格兰巴金哈姆爾","lifeSummary":"当Margaret Keynes于大约1292年出生在英国巴金哈姆爾时，她的父亲Robert Keynes27岁，母亲Alice24岁。她于1309年与Philip De Aylesbury在英国英格兰巴金哈姆爾米爾頓 凱恩斯结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和1个女儿的父母。她去世于1315年在她的家乡享年24岁。"},"hr":{"about 1292–1315":"oko 1292.–1315.","1292–1315":"1292–1315.","1276–1349":"1276–1349","1312–1359":"1312–1359","1314–1349":"1314–1349","1266–1295":"1266–1295.","1270–1295":"1270–1295.","about 1292":"oko 1292.","Bef 1314":"prije 1314.","1295":"1295.","Abt 1312":"oko 1312.","1270":"1270","1292":"1292","1291":"1291.","1349":"1349","1315":"1315.","1359":"1359","1314":"1314","1312":"1312","1266":"1266","1276":"1276","1309":"1309.","1317":"1317","Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England":"Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England","Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, England":"Buckinghamshire, England","Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, , England":"Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Middleton Keyes, Buckinghamshire, England":"Buckinghamshire, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"about 1292–1315":"okolo 1292–1315","1292–1315":"1292–1315","1276–1349":"1276–1349","1312–1359":"1312–1359","1314–1349":"1314–1349","1266–1295":"1266–1295","1270–1295":"1270–1295","about 1292":"okolo 1292","Bef 1314":"před 1314","1295":"1295","Abt 1312":"okolo 1312","1270":"1270","1292":"1292","1291":"1291","1349":"1349","1315":"1315","1359":"1359","1314":"1314","1312":"1312","1266":"1266","1276":"1276","1309":"1309","1317":"1317","Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, England":"Shalstone, Buckinghamshire, Anglie","Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, England":"Buckinghamshire, Anglie","Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, , England":"Milton Keynes, Buckinghamshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Middleton Keyes, Buckinghamshire, England":"Buckinghamshire, Anglie, United Kingdom"},"da":{"about 1292–1315":"omkring 1292–1315","1292–1315":"1292–1315","1276–1349":"1276–1349","1312–1359":"1312–1359","1314–1349":"1314–1349","1266–1295":"1266–1295","1270–1295":"1270–1295","about 1292":"omkring 1292","Bef 131